The paper focuses on image captioning, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The proposed method involves pre-training a text-to-image caption generator, which is a machine learning task that falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses using the pre-trained model for data augmentation in image retrieval, which is a task related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
